name: Angel
description:
In this 43rd edition they requested:
-Stop violence against trans women and gay men, as well as a record of hate crimes.
- Stop discrimination. Promote the legal autonomy of the council to prevent and eliminate discrimination in CDMX. Streamline processing times for gender changes.
- Promote information material in all the Pillars of Mexico City.
- Guarantee the participation of the community in public policies. Equal opportunities in the public institutions of the three powers of Mexico City.
- Guarantee the inclusion of the community in health policies.
